        </div>

        <h1 class="font-bungee text-xl uppercase tracking-wide w-96 md:w-[70%] lg:w-[50%] md:text-4xl">
          Discover the Stories in Our Yearbook
        </h1>
        <a href="https://caturnawa.unasfest.com/yb" target="_blank">
          <h1 class="mt-3 text-sm md:text-base bg-white px-6 font-inter font-medium text-black transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg md:mt-5 md:px-10 py-2 md:font-bold">
            Explore 2024 Yearbook
          </h1>
